parameters:
\SE[53]You brought a bed that looks like it's from outer space...
I-I'm tired...

\SE[20]Vita-san was such a hard worker, so I ended up relying on
her...

\SE[12]But, it's a bit in the way here... \!\SE[20]Um... could
you move it a little closer to the edge...?

\SE[15]Alright...! Leave it to me...\SE[17] Because I am
invincible...!!

I kind of thought it would be nice to live a peaceful life like
this.

It seems to be called a 'life support system.' It appears to
provide the body with necessary nutrients and oxygen. However,
I'm not quite sure about the exact mechanism.
